                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Important guidelines for students appearing in upcoming term end examinations...
                            </p>                            
                            <a href="#" class="text-custom hover:text-custom/80 font-medium">more</a>
                        </div>                        
                        <div class="border-b pb-4">
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Parent Teacher Meeting Schedule</h3>
